description: A dashboard for visualizing results from the k6.io load testing tool, using the InfluxDB exporter

targets.query: SELECT count("value") FROM http_reqs WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT count("value") FROM http_req_failed WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter AND "value" = 1
SELECT "value" FROM data_sent WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT "value" FROM data_received WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT mean("value") FROM "vus" WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT sum("value") FROM "http_reqs" WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT sum("value") FROM "http_req_failed" WHERE test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND $timeFilter AND "value" = 1 
GROUP BY time($__interval), "status" fill(none)
SELECT mean("value") FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT max("value") FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT median("value") FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT min("value") FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter and value > 0
SELECT percentile("value", 90) FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT percentile("value", 95) FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter
SELECT max("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

SELECT percentile("value", 95) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)

SELECT percentile("value", 90) FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT min("value") FROM /^$Measurement$/ WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter and value > 0 GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(none)
SELECT "value" FROM $Measurement WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter and value > 0

SELECT count("value"), min("value"), median("value"), max("value"), mean("value"), percentile("value", 95) FROM http_req_duration WHERE team =~ /^$team$/ AND test_name =~ /^$test_name$/ AND "group" =~ /^$group$/ AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
